Package: madr
Title: Post-processing for the Method of Anchored Distributions
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Heather", "Savoy", email = "frystacka@berkeley.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reads MAD# result databases, performs dimension reduction on
    inversion data, calculates likelihoods and posteriors, tests for convergence.
    Also generates plots and reports to summarize results.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
